# bit_xinfinity_milestone.png

## Purpose

This image acts as:
- the primary visual identity of the BIT-X∞ repository,
- a historical milestone artifact,
- and a symbolic marker for the beginning of the BIT-X∞ expeditionary axis.

---

## Suggested Contents

The image may include:
- BIT-X∞ title
- Boundary Expedition subtitle
- author identity
- adaptive runtime themes
- blockchain-style visual framing
- QR code linking to:
